OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FScott Mills was sacked by the BBC
OL,8,Fafter the corporation learned the
OL,9,Fpolice investigation into allegations
OL,10,Fof a historical sexual offence
OL,11,Finvolved a person under 16, it has
OL,12,Fbeen reported.
OL,14,FThe BBC has confirmed it knew about
OL,15,Fthe police investigation into Mills in
OL,16,F2017, but said it "acted decisively"
OL,17,Fafter receiving "new information" in
OL,18,Fthe weeks before his sacking.
OL,26,@xD@SOUxD@dO]yD@QOUyD@aO]
