OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FMills' sacking was announced on
OL,8,FMonday, with the corporation
OL,9,Fterminating his contracts on Friday,
OL,10,Fjust days after taking him off air.
OL,12,FIn a report on Wednesday, BBC News
OL,13,Fsaid: "It is not clear if BBC managers
OL,14,Fat the time of the investigation in
OL,15,F2017 knew the age - but current
OL,16,Fmanagement only became aware in recent
OL,17,Fweeks and took action. BBC News
OL,18,Funderstands."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
