PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FIn a statement sent to ITV News, a BBC
OL,8,Fspokesperson said the broadcaster had
OL,9,Fobtained "new information" relating to
OL,10,FMills, without making any reference to
OL,11,Fthe age of the alleged victim.
OL,13,F"We hope people understand that there
OL,14,Fis a limit to what we can say because
OL,15,Fwe have to be mindful of the rights of
OL,16,Fthose involved," the statement said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
