PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,F"What we can confirm is that in recent
OL,8,Fweeks, we obtained new information
OL,9,Frelating to Scott and we spoke
OL,10,Fdirectly with him. As a result, the
OL,11,FBBC acted decisively in line with our
OL,12,Fculture and values and terminated his
OL,13,Fcontracts on Friday 27 March.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
