OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,F"The BBC has made a significant
OL,8,Fcommitment to improve its culture,
OL,9,Fprocesses and standards. Last year,
OL,10,Ffollowing an independent culture
OL,11,Freview, we set out the behavioural
OL,12,Fexpectations for everyone who works
OL,13,Fwith or for the BBC and we were clear
OL,14,Faction would be taken if these were
OL,15,Fnot met.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
