PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,F"Separately, we can confirm the BBC
OL,8,Fwas made aware in 2017 of the
OL,9,Fexistence of an ongoing police
OL,10,Finvestigation, which was subsequently
OL,11,Fclosed in 2019 with no arrest or
OL,12,Fcharge being made. We are doing more
OL,13,Fwork to understand the detail of what
OL,14,Fwas known by the BBC at this time."
OL,16,FThe police investigation was closed in
OL,17,F2019 after prosecutors decided there
OL,18,Fwas insufficient evidence to bring
OL,19,Fcharges.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
