PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FIn his first public statement since
OL,8,Fnews broke of his sacking on Monday,
OL,9,FMills said he had co-operated fully
OL,10,Fwith the investigation, adding he has
OL,11,Fbeen the subject of "rumour and
OL,12,Fspeculation".
OL,14,FHe said: "The recent announcement that
OL,15,FI am no longer contracted to the BBC
OL,16,Fhas led to the publication of rumour
OL,17,Fand speculation. In response to this
OL,18,Fthe Metropolitan Police has made a
OL,19,Fstatement, which I confirm relates to
OL,20,Fme.
OL,26,@sD@UOUtD@LO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
