PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,F"An allegation was made against me in
OL,8,F2016 of a historic sexual offence
OL,9,Fwhich was the subject of a police
OL,10,Finvestigation in which I fully co-
OL,11,Foperated and responded to in 2018.
OL,13,F"As the police have stated, a file of
OL,14,Fevidence was submitted to the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service, which determined
OL,16,Fthat the evidential threshold had not
OL,17,Fbeen met to bring charges.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,F"Since the investigation related to an
OL,8,Fallegation that dates back nearly 30
OL,9,Fyears and the police investigation was
OL,10,Fclosed seven years ago, I hope that
OL,11,Fthe public and the media will
OL,12,Funderstand and respect my wish not to
OL,13,Fmake any further public comment on
OL,14,Fthis matter.
OL,16,F"I wish to thank from the bottom of my
OL,17,Fheart all those who have reached out
OL,18,Fto me with kindness, my former
OL,19,Fcolleagues, and my beloved listeners,
OL,20,Fwho I greatly miss."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
