OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police launched an
OL,13,Finvestigation into 53-year-old in 2016
OL,14,Fover allegations of serious sexual
OL,15,Foffences involving a teenage boy under
OL,16,F16 between 1997 and 2000.
OL,18,FMills was questioned under caution by
OL,19,Fofficers in July 2018 and The Sun has
OL,20,Freported that Mills denied the claims
OL,21,Fat the time and informed the BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
