OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775164268
OL,3,CBBC says it sacked Scott Mills after
OL,4,Clearning police probe involved boy
OL,5,Cunder-16
OL,7,FThe newspaper said BBC bosses decided
OL,8,Fnot to take the then-Radio 1 presenter
OL,9,Foff air at the time and the case was
OL,10,Fdropped in May 2019 because of lack of
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FHampshire Police said the sexual
OL,14,Foffences allegations were first
OL,15,Freported by a third party in 2016, and
OL,16,Fthat the force logged the details and
OL,17,Fpassed on information to the Met for
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
